f adoption in the long term, although some industrial\napplications have been published; 5) 140 NLP techniques, 66 NLP tools and 25\nNLP resources are extracted from the selected studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Apr 2020 16:03:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 09:49:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-08"}
